</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>plentymarkets</strong> = plentymarkets calculates the VAT and generates the invoice. You set up an event procedure which uploads the invoices to Amazon via Amazon IDU. See <a href="#3175">Setting up Amazon IDU</a>.<br></p>
</li>
