</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Quantity for items that are not limited to the stock</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">For items with the setting <strong>no limitation</strong>, the maximum amount of the real stock and the quantity defined here is transferred.<br>
<strong><em>Example:</em></strong> Setting 0, net stock 8\. plentymarkets transfers 8.<br>
Items with the setting <strong>Limited to net stock</strong> are not taken into consideration.</p></td>
