</table>
</div>
<div class="sect3">
<h4 id="600">3.2.4. Carrying out order settings</h4>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>In the <strong>Order settings</strong> tab, you carry out settings related to shipping.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The abbreviation MFN stands for merchant-fulfilled network. This means that the seller takes care of order processing. Watch this video tutorial for further information about Amazon MFN:</p>
</div>
<div class="videoblock">
<div class="title">Amazon MFN</div>
<div class="content">
<iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/307433826" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>
